    "name": "名录：爱丽丝的白鼠",
    "steam_appid": 3236930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236930/extras/31a5bb5b8590a56841002413e3862277.poster.avif?t=1772105483\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236930/extras/31a5bb5b8590a56841002413e3862277.webm?t=1772105483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236930/extras/31a5bb5b8590a56841002413e3862277.mp4?t=1772105483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将在人类灭绝的末世中扮演一位没有记忆的“生物”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你有手，可以握住武器。你有颗聪明的大脑，可收集情报和找到怪物们的弱点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从怪物所占领的实验室逃离，和它们战斗，去查明自己究竟是什么。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >废弃的实验室，千疮百孔的星球，变异的生物，各种离奇的入侵者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你，在此世界中诞生的“小白鼠”，你想要什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236930/extras/8a26d853fc98f5409de1d6bc4eb93f30.poster.avif?t=1772105483\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236930/extras/8a26d853fc98f5409de1d6bc4eb93f30.webm?t=1772105483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集信息，寻找敌人的弱点，控制武器攻向正确的方向，格挡、反击、闪躲？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是近战还是消耗不多的能源进行远程打击？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >去战斗，厮杀，演算失败后的一次次重启，最后从收集的信息中拼凑出原住民“人类”灭绝的真相，入侵者们的去向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236930/extras/0cf6354b02785b4fae6a00624c0da158.poster.avif?t=1772105483\" width=900 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236930/extras/0cf6354b02785b4fae6a00624c0da158.webm?t=1772105483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236930/extras/0cf6354b02785b4fae6a00624c0da158.mp4?t=1772105483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏基本操作：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●鼠标可以控制镜头和武器攻击的方向（以便攻击弱点）；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●双击移动键消耗能量进行冲刺（闪避）动作；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●使用药品恢复生命值；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●调整背包重量或暂时丢弃背包以提高敏捷度；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●在战斗中，要权衡是否使用会留下“后遗症”的攻击或防御药水；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●消耗能量来提升等级或发动强力射击；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
